No. 138. No. 180,

Misc.

Idlewild Bon Voyage Liquor Corp. v. Epstein [formerly Rohan] et al.; and Idlewild Bon Voyage Liquor Corp. v. Bicks et al., U. S. District Court Judges. Charles H. Tuttle for petitioner. Louis J. Lefkowitz, Attorney General of New York, Paxton Blair, Solicitor General, and Julius L. Sack-man for respondents in No. 138.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit granted in No. 138, and motion for leave to file petition for writ of mandamus granted in No. 180, Misc.

Reported below: 289 F. 2d 426.
